What is PWA
1. A progressive web app (PWA) delivers an app-like native experience through your mobile phoneâ€™s browser.
2. They have no particular affiliation to any one device
3. Developers no longer need to write separate code for Android and Apple devices.

Reduced Friction to the user
1. Native mobile apps have to be downloaded from the store
2. Users have to wait for the App to download
3. The App needs permissions to function properly

